text: D nitni i ijehlen. Swexxoen kwen si Loamaa n Leaoam, ugin ad iawev usfel s amkan is. Lemmer macci d lmumnin, argaz tameiiut, ur ten tessinem, a ten teazem ur teeoim; segsen a d tegwrim di le$ouo - ni$ Oebbi Issekcam s aeunu S, win i S ihwan - lemmer mfaoaqen, yili, war ccekk, Nesaadda, $ef wid segsen ijehlen, aaaqeb aqeoean
